- Make the game limited in terms of gameplay:
    - The user starts the game with a limited amount of darts which they can set between 0 and 100 (training mode)
- Make difficulty settings:
    - Hard: Fewer darts, faster balloons
    - Medium: Moderate darts, moderate balloon speed
    - Easy: More darts, slower balloons
- Create a score system:
    - Keep track of players and their scores by player name and score 
    - top 10 scores are shown at the bottom of the menu
